media-label-images - Image Rating Labels

USAGE:
    media-label-images

DESCRIPTION:
    Label images with star ratings based on directory location:
    - Images in 'bad' directories: rating 1 (consider for deletion)
    - Images in 'good' directories: rating 3
    - Images in 'selected' directories: rating 4

RATING SYSTEM:
    1 - Bad (consider for deletion)
    3 - Good
    4 - Selected

NOTE:
    Processes symbolic links in /media/output directory structure.

EXAMPLES:
    media-label-images
